name: Dr. Nasim Moarefi
about: Our family dental office is located in Surrey, British Columbia, and we are proud to be your local dentist. Our office will gladly go the extra mile to make you feel comfortable and relaxed during your visit. From dental exams and cleanings to cosmetic dentistry, our office’s only goal is keeping our patients happy. We are dedicated to providing professional dental care to all of our patients, and we can’t wait to see you at your appointment.

clinic.name: Central City Surrey Dentist
clinic.description: Our dental office is a clean, well-equipped space where a skilled team provides a variety of dental services focused on patient comfort, education, and overall oral health—supported by strong teamwork and organized administrative care.
